####  Macro name: Multi-Channel Image Lite beta v0.1
####  Consolidates all open images into a single multi-channel image.  ##  Closes the open images, leaving only the resulting image open. 
############################################################# 

Create new image
destImage = ZenImage()

## Obtain count of open images for purpose of looping through the open images
imageNumber = Zen.Application.Documents.Count

## Loop through the open images, adding each as an new channel to the destImage
for i in range(0, imageNumber):    
  sourceImage = Zen.Application.Documents.ActiveDocument    
  destImage.AddSubImage(sourceImage, 0, i, 0)    
  Zen.Application.Documents.ActiveDocument.Close()
Zen.Application.Documents.Add(destImage)
